### Category - Create
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "categoryName": "Outdoor Gear",
  "description": "Equipment for camping and hiking adventures",
  "imageUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/images/categories/outdoor-gear.png",
}

###
### Category - Update
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 1,
  "categoryName": "Outdoor & Travel",
  "description": "Camping, hiking, and travel-ready products",
  "imageUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/images/categories/outdoor-travel.png",
}

###
### Category - Delete
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1
Accept: application/json

